{"TopicId":145203,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"SPH/VAB Scenery Synchronization","CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-01T14:47:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-01T14:47:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery simple idea. When it is \u0022night\u0022 as measured by the game clock, have the scenery from inside the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E also be night, like the outside.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv data-role=\u0022contentPage\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImages to illustrate point: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/23XvK\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/a/23XvK\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would be a small thing, but I think it would be nice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"foamyesque","CreatedById":2982,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-01T21:56:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E and the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E use just as much computer juice as flight does, why not just go whole hog and have the background include \u003Cem\u003Eeverything\u003C/em\u003E, such as, for example, the \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003Esmoking wreck\u003C/span\u003E reason you\u0027re back in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E :v\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-01T23:12:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI fully agree this should be in stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nJust in case you were not aware though.\u00A0 There is a mod for that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/102558-105-lightsout-v015-daynight-mode-in-vabsph/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattinoz","CreatedById":118580,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-01T23:25:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E is a magic land were time has no meaning that is why I think it\u0027s always day time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T02:37:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222700757\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145203\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470093904\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022118580\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mattinoz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, mattinoz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E is a magic land were time has no meaning that is why I think it\u0027s always day time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen shouldn\u0027t it be raining 5D bookshelves outside?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattinoz","CreatedById":118580,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T04:31:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222700945\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145203\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470105447\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen shouldn\u0027t it be raining 5D bookshelves outside?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean you can\u0027t see them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T11:36:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEven though game time stops in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E (and, in contrast, REAL time passes very quickly) it would be a nice touch if the \u0027view of outside from inside\u0027 matched the \u0027view of outside from outside\u0027 at the time you go inside.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn short, yes I agree with the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T11:39:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrom a game play perspective I\u0027m not a huge fan of having to build in the dark.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe lights inside the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u00A0at night would have to be bright enough to give similar illumination as you would see in day time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you look at the images of the day/night mod mentioned earlier in this thread, it looks way too dark in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E at night to be practical.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T11:49:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222701301\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145203\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470137981\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrom a game play perspective I\u0027m not a huge fan of having to build in the dark.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe lights inside the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u00A0at night would have to be bright enough to give similar illumination as you would see in day time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you look at the images of the day/night mod mentioned earlier in this thread, it looks way too dark in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E at night to be practical.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou do raise a good point. If good illumination was used, I think this might not be a big problem then.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T13:30:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe idea in principle is good, but seeing as lights in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E are one of the direct causes of CPU/GPU being pushed harder than in flight mode, I\u0027d rather not have a day/night cycle that would force me to have lights on while editing a craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA day/night toggle to do a quick check of what our craft looks like in the dark, like the mentioned mod does, now that I would be ok with being stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T13:47:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222701421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145203\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470144625\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA day/night toggle to do a quick check of what our craft looks like in the dark, like the mentioned mod does, now that I would be ok with being stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m all for this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOptions are always better than changes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGive us a button in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u00A0that toggles day/night mode for purely testing lighting setups on crafts. Then give us a toggle\u00A0option in the game play menu for \u0022auto day/night switch in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0022 so those that want it to match the time of day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TwinKerbal","CreatedById":161536,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-02T23:26:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you use hangar extension you get to whack a kerbal the buildings outside and they show up at the space center as destroyed. I don\u0027t see why it would be too hard, since you can destroy buildings.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-05T03:09:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222702083\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145203\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470180383\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161536\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TwinKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/2/2016 at 7:26 PM, TwinKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you use hangar extension you get to whack a kerbal the buildings outside and they show up at the space center as destroyed. I don\u0027t see why it would be too hard, since you can destroy buildings.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that is also stock, no?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TwinKerbal","CreatedById":161536,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-05T05:19:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt might be.\u00A0 I don\u0027t know, it\u0027s been a while since I played stock in general.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}